```r
cytokinePCoAMeta %>%
  group_by(k4) %>%
  summarise(k4.Dim1 = mean(Dim1),
            k4.Dim2 = mean(Dim2)) -> k4Centroid

ggplot(cytokinePCoAMeta,
       aes(x = Dim1,
           y = Dim2,
           color = k4)) +
  geom_point(size = 2,
             alpha = 0.5) +
  stat_ellipse(type = \t\") +
